Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi, everyone, we're going \Nto start Kaleido Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, please \Nkeep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, do you \Nhave someone you like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He makes your heart ache. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's someone you exchange diaries \Nwith and hold hands with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, I hope I fall in love \Nwith someone wonderful too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope! I hope...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Ken, why are you crying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dare mo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dokoka ni aru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja nai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saigo made yareru to ittetane {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kitto tsuyogatte itanda {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Itsudatte muchabakka de zutto karamawari de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakedo anata dake ga soba ni ita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Daremo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arukidaseru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koko kara nanika ga hajimaru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shinjite itai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mada minu hikari yakusoku \Nno basho e to tsuzuite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, wake up, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:47.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Diva's Amazing Love."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because it's your day off,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't mean you should keep \Nsleeping as long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'd been working at \NTheatrical Camp until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You met Pamela, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She showed me an amazing maneuver of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the success rate of \Nthat maneuver was very low,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she was seldom allowed \Nto do it in a real show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true. If she failed that \Nmaneuver, it wouldn't be surprising.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I actually saw that, \Nit was like I saw a miracle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It just gave me chills. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jumping straight up and grabbing \Nthe same swing she jumped from...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if the Legendary \NGreat Maneuver is like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Kaleido Stage \Nwasn't a suitable place for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's finished. Thanks, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a Dorm Supervisor is not an easy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Please be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. This is it. Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah Dupont.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they mass media people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running away, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do, Miss Sarah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please run away by yourself, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why do I have to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here for you, my eternal diva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah Dupont,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the rumor is true that you're moving \Nto Andy Lowe's major label, ADX?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I already said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about \NKalos, he already said okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is it true you are dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pose for us as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure we both look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be nice enough to \Nstop right here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for any other questions, \Nthis girl will answer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is their relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I don't! I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I can't help you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were talking about Miss \NSarah moving to a major label.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not leaving \NKaleido Stage, I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Miss Sarah is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the mass media people \Naren't coming here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they left as soon as they found out \Nthat I wasn't interested in talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. From ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture of Andy, Kalos and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah, Mr. Andy and Kalos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good, tight muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fill the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he look so nice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, we were always hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our hearts were filled with dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy was into writing music.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was into singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Kalos was aiming to be a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos was the most popular among us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he became popular enough that he \Ncould have his own show in Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He injured his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough to perform magic again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got the insurance money from the \Npolicy he had taken out on his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos used that as startup capital for \NKaleido Stage, another dream of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He spent everything he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he extreme?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I followed Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos told me not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was obvious that he was just bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Sarah, weren't \Nyou aiming to be a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you followed Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You were in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fill the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The image I have in mind \Nis completely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course, I'm still in love, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was hiding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe it's only natural \Nthat other people can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, did you give up \Nyour dream for the Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's not like I gave up my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream just changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those days, I wished I could \Nsing for everybody in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoy singing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think this is the \Nplace best suited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the feeling that I'm needed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is something I can't replace \Nwith anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid he no longer needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure Miss Sarah was crying back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless the Boss stops her, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure Miss Sarah will move \Nto Mr. Andy's recording company.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss... Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to talk about!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ignored me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on? It's you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman, which way \Ndid the Boss's car go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're running after a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miss Sarah is in love with Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never can judge people \Nby the way they look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Miss Sarah is facing a big decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a very expensive restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, how can he go out and have a \Ngourmet meal in this kind of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Let's get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,back then, all you thought of was magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all you care about is Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're really okay about Sarah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't need her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I stood no chance against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can introduce Sarah to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I sincerely love Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give a toast to me and Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is in our cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without asking how Miss Sarah feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why are you making decisions as you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't! Please listen to my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will not! Please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse. Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't! Please listen to my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are just alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse. Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I {\i1}won't{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until you listen to my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we listen to what she has to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Kalos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, Miss Sarah loves Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lying when you \Nsay that you don't need her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I gain by telling a lie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible, saying something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me a question. So I \Njust answered with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you needed her when you established \NKaleido Stage ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even now, you must...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what she tells herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall ever saying \Neven a word like that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're really saying that you \Njust used Sarah for ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, I thought you were a very \Ndifficult, unreasonable, scary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and unpleasant man who doesn't \Nlisten to others, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you created such a \Nwonderful Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you must have a good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you were so cold-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I have things to \Ntake care of. I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pick up Sarah sometime today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure that it's okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy called and said he would be \Nhere to pick me up by evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, pretty soon, I'll be an \Nartist for the ADX label!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd want to have \Na cheerful farewell party,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but... I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah, you don't mind doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm really not sure right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I've known Kalos for ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he has never once lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kalos told me that he \Ndidn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think he really meant what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you send me off, please \Ndo it cheerfully with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at dealing with gloomy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a little more work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can ask the moving company \Nto take care of the big stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll need the {\i1}nunchaku {\i0}and \NChinese broadsword right away, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah's picture is \Nalready on the ADX home page.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no stopping it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone you trusted says \Nhe doesn't need you anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be unbearable to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to what I heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,many recording companies have \Ntried to recruit her in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that the Boss never \Nsaid anything until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why the Boss said \Nsomething like that only now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she suddenly lost value to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, there are \Nquite a lot of Sarah fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm pretty sure it'll \Ndamage our sales figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a love triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet their relationship is too \Ncomplicated to be described in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love entangled during \Nten years. Love! Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah's growing love \Nfor Kalos. Love! Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Andy's love for Miss \NSarah. Love! Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos withdraws because of \Nhis love. Love! Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just then, in front of Miss Sarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a flash of lightning, \Nappears the girl, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troubled Miss Sarah's love, love, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, don't you think that maybe \Nthe Boss withdrew himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything would certainly make \Nsense if you thought of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we should leave \Neverything the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again. Sora's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we stick our nose in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Let me think about it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's an interesting card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't stick to one idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the possibilities will be infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me, Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really know what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are the only ones to send me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a message for you from Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says if you want to know \Nhow the Boss feels about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please come to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I already know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the mysterious Fool, Magical Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my magic, I will find \Nout your true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, she has no clue what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, find anything related to Miss Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to get out, \Nyou should tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this nonsense about \Ntelling the truth?! I never lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stop until I find out \Nwhat you think of Miss Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if it's my business or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't have a chance \Nto sing here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, allow me to speak on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sarah, please don't go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I need you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you, Sarah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please keep singing for \NKaleido Stage, Sarah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any special \Nfeelings towards Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the picture \Nsitting over there, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What! When did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't underestimate the \Npower of the Magical Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you still keep that ten-year-old photo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from when the three of you were together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never tell Sarah what I'm going to say now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, even after that, I needed Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage needed Sarah's songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I needed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when things didn't go well, \Nand when I was having hard times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was always beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't imagine not having her beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may sound conceited,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I tell her that I \Ndon't need her anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she can go after her dream \Nwithout reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I didn't have the courage to \Ntell even a simple lie like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the courage to lose her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've robbed her for ten years of the \Nchance to make her dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the offer came from Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he can make her dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware that I need Sarah now, and \Neven in the future, I will need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't want her to \Nknow about this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a farce this has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're tired of Kalos, call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you care about Sarah, don't \Ntell her what I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Microphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave you two alone. Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you really have no clue, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a chance to sing on the world stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't decide my dream \Nwithout consulting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Kaleido Stage much \Nmore than the world stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, Sora... And whenever \Nwe have newcomers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like singing here more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone, this is the \Nfirst show after our vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's brace ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curtain's rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came here to see your regretful face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, suddenly, my junior high \Nschool classmate came to the U.S.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But something seems wrong with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, you don't mind coming \Nalong with me, do you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Yuri asked me out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Er... uh... well... Oh, \Ndear. Oh, dear. Oh, dear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, \N"An Amazing Sinister Rumor."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
